column2: "What an idiot. After all he's been through, he still doesn't know when to quit."
"And you're pretty trusting to take his request. But, hey, it's none of my business."
"You've probably already figured it out, but this is no normal place."
"The reason? I don't know. That stupid old hag said something about the photons being weird."
"I really don't know anything. If you want to know, you're going to have to ask the self-proclaimed protector about it."
"Where is she? Hell if I know!"

"Alright, I'm heading out.
Umm... where was it again...?"

"Me? Lost?
Like I would ever get lost..."
